OL,6,FWhistleblowers at one of England's     
OL,7,Fworst performing hospital trusts have  
OL,8,Fsaid a climate of fear among staff is  
OL,9,Fputting patients at risk.              
OL,11,FFormer and current clinicians at       
OL,12,FUniversity Hospitals Birmingham (UHB)  
OL,13,FNHS Trust allege they were punished by 
OL,14,Fmanagement for raising safety concerns,
OL,15,Fa BBC Newsnight investigation found.   
OL,17,FOne insider said the trust was "a bit  
OL,18,Flike the mafia".                       
OL,20,FThe trust said it took "patient safety 
OL,21,Fvery seriously".                       
